<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Definition and objectives of accounting, uniform accounting system, accounting system and subsystems (parts of accounting), functions of accounting, users of accounting information, basic accounting
concepts, the concept of account in accounting, definition and form of account, classification of accounts and rules of operation. Recording tools in accounting.</Data></Cell>
