<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Technical Equipment Necessary to Create a Portable or Room-Type Studio
Audio Recording and Editing Programs
Selection and Preparation of the Venue where the Voice-over will be Performed
Improvement of Reading Ability
Basic Diction Training
Acting Education
Microphone Technique
Voice Acting
Correction of Possible Errors in the Text and Editing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425118&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
