<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course;
Testing the entrepreneurship feature, How to find a business idea? Concept of responsible entrepreneurship and sharing of experience with business idea development and creativity exercises.
Concept of responsible entrepreneurship and sharing of experience with business idea development and creativity exercises.
Workshops on the business model.
Canvas business model application studies
Creating customer personas and customer maps.
Problem solving methods.
Business concept, business functions, types, forms of establishment, financial and legal responsibilities.
Business Plan Concept and Elements: Market research, Marketing plan, Production plan, management plan, Financial plan
How to prepare a business plan, Workshops on the business plan,
Evaluation of Entrepreneurship Course and Brainstorming
includes topics.</Data></Cell>
