<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 201</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Services Management I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health concept and determinants; environment, heredity, lifestyle , health effects, Health Management definition, objectives, scope and importance, health services, health systems, health services, what are the systems and institutions that produce Turkey&apos;s health system and sub-systems with objectives, organizational structure, current status and operation of the hospital, the definition and objectives of the hospital, functions and characteristics that distinguish hospitals from other institutions and organizations ,classification and functioning of hospitals historical development of the profession of hospital management and characteristics that should be in the hospital manager hospital management and organization, as well as departments and functions of the hospital. Recent developments in the hospital sector and the effects of these developments on hospital management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 213</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Economics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To give basic information about the application of economic theory, concepts and methods to the health sector.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425013&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 215</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cost Accounting in Healthcare Organizations</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The place of cost accounting in the accounting system. Definition of cost accounting. Objectives of cost accounting. Establishment and operation stages of cost accounting in health institutions. Cost and Elements - Cost, Expense, Loss, Expenditure, Expenditure, Revenue concepts and relationships between them. Place of Expense and expense types in cost accounting.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425014&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 223</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biostatistics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic concepts of statistics, statistical methods specific to health, field research and reporting.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425005&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
