<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 255</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Application in Health Services I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+40+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To increase the practical experience of the students about the occupations they are studying, to know the health sector and business life, to establish business relations for the future and to transfer the knowledge acquired in the undergraduate education into practice.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 224</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Decision Making in Health Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course covers decision-making processes in healthcare institutions, decision-making under uncertainty, group decisions, decision support systems, and multi-criteria decision-making methods. Through case studies, students learn to analyze strategic, financial, and operational decisions in healthcare services. Additionally, the course explores cognitive biases affecting the decision quality of healthcare managers, ethical dilemmas, and data-driven decision support applications.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425084&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 231</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Effective Presentation and Communication Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Within the scope of the course, the concept of communication, elements of the communication process, verbal and non-verbal communication, effective communication techniques, factors that prevent and facilitate communication, active listening and feedback, presentation definition, presentation planning, presentation content preparation, presentation preparation, effective presentation techniques will be discussed.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425116&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 275</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Managerial Epidemiology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to epidemiology, health indicators used in epidemiology, epidemiological studies-I, epidemiological research-II, data collection and evaluation in epidemiology, epidemiology in epidemiology, epidemiology of chronic diseases, epidemiology of infectious diseases, evidence-based medicine (CDT) and clinical epidemiology, health records, disease and reporting of deaths, epidemiology, health policy and planning Epidemiological research planning, Epidemiological research presentation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=424999&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 285</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">International Marketing</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Marketing, the concept of marketing in health services, characteristics of health services marketing differences from other industries, the history and factors affecting the development of health services marketing, the reasons for health services marketing. Sunday Sunday The concepts of consumer, customer and patient, Consumer behavior; Market Segmentation and Demand Management in the Healthcare Market, Classification of Consumers and the Main Factors Affecting Consumer Behavior, Types of Consumer Purchasing Behavior, marketing research in healthcare.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=425001&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Care Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 288</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Logistics Management in Health Care</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Input definition, material management cycle and scope in healthcare production. Purchasing in health services, purchase of capital goods, tender preparation and contract preparation, inventory management, demand and consumption estimates, hospital warehouse management, hospital pharmacy management, transportation, use and sterile processes, consumption, recycling and medical waste management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=424957&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
