<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Primary care services, family medicine system, long-term health care services, home care, terminal care, elderly care services. Development and organization of health services in Turkey, Health Transformation Program, Development and organization of health services in Turkey, patient rights and Ethics in Health Enterprises, problems and effects of health workers (burnout, job satisfaction). Mobbing problems and effects, Health Development and upgrade, globalization and health.</Data></Cell>
