<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health information management and technologies, evaluation of health services, health management information systems, electronic health records, basic components of corporate electronic health record systems, information technologies for chronic disease management, national health information systems and networks, information systems in private health insurance</Data></Cell>
