<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1. Providing information about health law and related basic concepts
2. Providing information on patient rights within the framework of national and international legislation
3. Informed consent in medical interventions and general information about medical malpractice
4. Explaining administrative, civil and criminal responsibilities of health professionals
5. Learning the concept of personal health data
6. Raising awareness of mobbing in health</Data></Cell>
