<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">SYB 392</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Policies and Comparative Health Systems</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course consists of two main topics
1. Health policy; health policy related to the basic concepts and definitions, the relationship of Country policies and Health Systems Planning and policy in health care, health policies, and in the process creating strategic approaches, decentralization in health care practices, implementation and evaluation of health policies, health policies and the relationships between globalization, international organizations and their impact on public policy.
2.Methods of obtaining useful results through the study, classification and comparison of inter-country health systems within the framework of comparative health systems.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=424994&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
