<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Gain the experience of being able to address a scientific topic in different aspects without prejudice, analyze it together with its opponents (analysis), reveal a comment by revealing the reaction of society to the topic, and summarize the discussion in plain language so that everyone can understand it, whether they are an expert on the topic or not</Data></Cell>
