<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize photo processing programs, explain the basic features of Photoshop software, define the process of visual preparation before printing. Describe the relationship between the tools and menus of the software in image preparation, apply program usage information at basic level, discuss the results of basic image preparation studies. and design a visual image for printing and the web.</Data></Cell>
