<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Making Audiobooks</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Microphone Technique
* Differences in the use of dynamic and condenser microphones
* Setting and maintaining the correct distance and angle with the microphone
* Determination of the minimum and maximum sound intensity
* The sound of letters that are likely to explode on the microphone
